data.description: Welcome to this Beautiful Home located in Driftwood Estates! Walk into the spacious living room with updated flooring, fresh painting then continue on to the open floor plan that is perfect for entertaining! Dining room/family room provides so much space for family time or just a quiet movie night. Split Bedrooms provide all the privacy each family member desires. HVAC is 3-4 years old, duct work has recently been serviced, HWH 2018, new LVP flooring, new carpet in bedrooms and interior painting in all rooms. Driftwood Estates offers the ultimate family living with the community pool and the neighborhood activities that are planned throughout the year. Call today to view this awesome home!
